  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654680/extras/66565a22d23a0e80c6ba06af3328511e.poster.avif?t=1747895206\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654680/extras/66565a22d23a0e80c6ba06af3328511e.webm?t=1747895206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654680/extras/66565a22d23a0e80c6ba06af3328511e.mp4?t=1747895206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Welcome to the frenzied arena of Khuga Bash! A multiplayer action brawler game from the universe of Khuga. Take control of this cute but deadly fighter cats who's on a mission to prove their combat prowess. In Khuga Bash, it's not just about luck; it's about proving you're the ultimate champion of the Khugaverse!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥊 <strong>Battle Ferocious Bosses:</strong> Go toe-to-toe with ferocious bosses as you venture deeper into the heart of the Khugaverse. Can you out-punch them all?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆<strong> Fight for Supremacy:</strong> Climb the leaderboards, rack up the highest scores, and make your mark as the reigning Khuga combat champion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👊 <strong>Intense Combat:</strong> Engage in adrenaline-pumping combat with lightning-fast action, powerful combos, and a range of combat styles to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌐<strong> Explore the Arena:</strong> Immerse yourself in the dynamic Khuga arena, each battle more intense and challenging than the last.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654680/extras/66565a22d23a0e80c6ba06af3328511e.poster.avif?t=1747895206\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654680/extras/66565a22d23a0e80c6ba06af3328511e.webm?t=1747895206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654680/extras/66565a22d23a0e80c6ba06af3328511e.mp4?t=1747895206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Welcome to the frenzied arena of Khuga Bash! A multiplayer action brawler game from the universe of Khuga. Take control of this cute but deadly fighter cats who's on a mission to prove their combat prowess. In Khuga Bash, it's not just about luck; it's about proving you're the ultimate champion of the Khugaverse!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥊 <strong>Battle Ferocious Bosses:</strong> Go toe-to-toe with ferocious bosses as you venture deeper into the heart of the Khugaverse. Can you out-punch them all?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆<strong> Fight for Supremacy:</strong> Climb the leaderboards, rack up the highest scores, and make your mark as the reigning Khuga combat champion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👊 <strong>Intense Combat:</strong> Engage in adrenaline-pumping combat with lightning-fast action, powerful combos, and a range of combat styles to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌐<strong> Explore the Arena:</strong> Immerse yourself in the dynamic Khuga arena, each battle more intense and challenging than the last.</p>",
